    "body" : "<p>You could use a <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/io/StringReader.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">StringReader</a> and convert the reader to an input stream using the solution in <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/62241/how-to-convert-a-reader-to-inputstream-and-a-writer-to-outputstream\">this other stackoverflow post</a>.</p>\n"
