    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can try <a href=\"https://github.com/yegor256/cactoos/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">cactoos</a> for that.</p>\n<pre><code>final InputStream input = new InputStreamOf(&quot;example&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>The object is created with <code>new</code> and not a static method for <a href=\"https://www.yegor256.com/2017/11/14/static-factory-methods.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">a reason</a>.</p>\n"
